<C>__{blake}
<D>__{one minute, could i please talk to you for one minute...look look look: i broke up with my girlfriend...}
<A>__{angle exterior the vestibule. the young asian girl, now walking with a male friend, pass in front of the vestibule. beyond them we see blake and scott, as blake motions to the mailbox, and moves to the mailbox and takes out a letter. angle interior the vestibule. on scott, as he watches blake take a letter out of the jimmied mailbox.}
